transcription: Becky Lynch wins Royal Rumble in shocking fashion, WWE fans lose their minds. The man was not scheduled to be in the contest but due to an ankle injury suffered by Lana on the kickoff show she was granted entry into the match. And from the moment she entered the WWE fans at Chase Field were behind her.  for the win. The final three were Lynch, Flair and Nia Jax with the last kicker eliminating both to book her place at WrestleMania. She will now choose either Raw Women's Champion Ronda Rousey or SmackDown Women's Champion Asuka as her opponent. More to follow.
